Description of the files:

run_boston.py -- Test of the GCP method for the Boston data set with 5% of outlier
run_boston_cv.py -- Cross-validation over 50 folds of the GCP method for the Boston data set with 5% of outlier
CPNetwork.py -- Theano based implementation of the GCP method
distributions.py -- Auxiliary methods for KL divergences
optimizer_setup.py -- Auxiliary methods for setting up the optimizier
special_functions.py -- Theano implementation of the function Psi 
